milestones.description: Rick McCosker has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for AUS, going past Graeme Watson's 1
Ian Chappell has broken the record for most sixes (7) in ODIs, going past Chris Old's 6
Greg Chappell has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for AUS, going past Ian Chappell
Keith Boyce has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for WI, going past Fredericks
Alvin Kallicharran and Viv Richards's 92-run partnership is the highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 89 between Mike Denness and Chris Old
Julien has conceded the most runs in an innings (66) in ODIs for WI, going past Holder's record of 65
Alvin Kallicharran and Viv Richards's 92-run partnership is WI's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 15 between Clive Lloyd and Viv Richards
Ian Chappell has scored 6 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, breaking Fletcher's record
